The target assembly consisted of natural Sc, Ti, V, Fe,
Co and Cu foils, thickness between 10 and 20 mu,
purity 99.9-99.999%,surrounded by 50 mu aluminium foils
of high purity used as monitors for proton beam.
The dimensions of the aluminium foils and of the
targets were 20*20 mm.

x4code.headerHelp: Error in value of quantity, defined under ERR-ANALYS

x4freetext: The mean values of the errors were obtained
by  root-mean-square addition of the individual errors
for the various experiments - 2 and 3 of them in
general - and of the standard deviation of the mean.
Any analysis of individual errors is absent.
